 a numerical integration of the FKPP equation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2019 18:54:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 4 Aug 2020 12:21:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-07"}
