ities of echo-chamber\nformation. We also found that the restricted reconnection case reduced the\nchances of echo chamber formation and led to smaller echo chambers.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2019 02:24:55 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Apr 2020 20:38:45 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 30 Jul 2020 13:12:56 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 11 Nov 2020 16:42:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-17"}
