 another type of superconducting\ncorrelation is enhanced inside the ferromagnetic phase. We discuss a possible\nrelation between our results and reentrant superconductivity in U-based\nferromagnetic superconductors under transverse magnetic fields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2019 05:58:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 6 Dec 2019 08:29:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-05-20"}
