se times at which the\nrelative phase of the imposed spirals with respect to the bar becomes equal to\n\\pm\\pi/2. A connection of these effects to the phenomenon of recurrent spirals\nis discussed.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2019 11:06:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-22"}
