 where\nover-dispersed count datasets are commonplace. In order to facilitate the use\nof these methods within the wider medical community, user interfaces for both\nstudy planning and analysis of existing datasets are freely provided along with\nour open-source code via: http://www.fecrt.com/framework\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2019 11:51:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-16"}
