ity of our\nproposed methods in order to correct and provide HR monitoring post-calibrated\nwith high accuracy, raising further awareness of individual fitness in the\ndaily application.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 14 Oct 2019 17:24:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Oct 2019 04:57:51 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 14 Dec 2019 16:59:20 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Mon, 17 Feb 2020 07:29:17 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Thu, 5 Mar 2020 07:48:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-11"}
