on the quantum experiment science\nsatellite platform. Moreover, our SPDs open new windows of opportunities for\nspace research and applications in deep-space optical communications,\nsingle-photon laser ranging, as well as for testing the fundamental principles\nof physics in space.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2019 12:06:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-08"}
